This program displays the first initial of my first name, pauses, and then displays the first initial of my last name:

To compile the program, enter the follow line of code, on cisc210.cis.udel.edu:
    gcc -o rjsexton rjsexton.c -lncurses

To run the executable enter the following on cisc210.cis.udel.edu:
    ./rjsexton

The first initial of my first name has a background color of BLACK and a foreground color of WHITE
The first initial of my last name has a background color of GREEN and a foreground color of WHITE
